                          angular front end developer 


                          basic ccommand 

                1.to create project - ng new project - name /ng new project name -- rouuting 

                2. to run  a project ng - serve /ng serve -- open

                3.to create componenet - ng g c componenet- name 

                
                4.to create service - ng g s  service- name 

                5.to creative directives- ng g d directive-name
                          
                          
                          
                          
                          
                          
                          
                          
                          
                          
                          Basic concepts

1.component-to create {html,css,ts file} root component- app componenet

2.module - to add libraries to the project - root module - app module 

3.data binding - data sharing between html and ts

    3.1 one way binding
        
        3.1.1 componenet to view

                    3.1.1.1 string interpolation : syntax -{{variable -name}}
            
                    3.1.1.2 property binding: [attribute]="variable-name"
        
        3.1.2 view to component
                     
                     3.1.2.1 event binding-(event)="function-call()"

                     3.1.2.2 event binding using $event - (event)="function-call($event)"

                     3.1.2.3 template reference variable - syntax: #variable-name 

    3.2 two way binding

        3.2 using ngModel - import FormModule in appModule, 
            syntax:[(ngModel)]="variable-name"
            
4.to set up path for a componenet : defined in app routing module

    syntax:{path:'',componenet:componenetClassName}

5.dependancy injection - to share data between classes

6.angular services -  for ridundant data


7. ngSubmit- to submit entire form syntax : (ngSubmit)="function-call"

8.Angular forms

            8.1 template driven forms - first design html
            
            8.2 model driven forms - first create model in ts

                8.2.1 reactive forms -add validation : import reactiveformsmodule

                    - form group - form builder + dependancy inject  ,form array ,form control



  9.angular directives-to manipulate DOM

    9.1  component directives

    9.2 structure directives - to change DOM stracture

        9.2.1 ngIf - syntax: *ngIf="condition"    

        9.2.2 ngFor - syntax " *ngFor="iteraor of array -name"

    9.3 Attribute Directive  - to apply set of style to html

        9.3.1 Predifined - eg: ngClass

        9.3.2 Userdefined

10.Locall storage -to permenently store data in browser

    10.1 setItem()

    10.2 getItem()

    10.3 removeItem()

11.angular pipes : to convert the data format


        syntax: expression | pipe operator [pipe arguments]

12.Animation

13.Parent-Child Communication


        13.1 parent to child  : input decorator

        13.2 child to parent : output decorator

14.event emitter - to generate userdefined events

        14.1 emit() - to occure the event 